OL,3,CStarmer denies he threatened Speaker
OL,4,Cover chaotic Gaza ceasefire vote
OL,6,FThe Speaker broke with procedure on
OL,7,FWednesday, allowing the Labour Party
OL,8,Fto amend an SNP motion calling for a
OL,9,FGaza ceasefire. Deputy Political
OL,10,FEditor Anushka Asthana reports
OL,12,FBy ITV News Westminster Producer, Maya
OL,13,FBowles
OL,15,FSir Keir Starmer has denied he
OL,16,F"threatened the Speaker in any way"
OL,17,Fover the Gaza ceasefire vote which
OL,18,Fdescended into chaos in the Commons on
OL,19,FWednesday night.
