OL,6,FSir Lindsay is facing calls from
OL,7,FConservatives and the SNP to resign
OL,8,Fover his handling of the debate, which
OL,9,Fresulted in MPs passing Labour's
OL,10,Famendment calling for an "immediate
OL,11,Fhumanitarian ceasefire" amid scenes of
OL,12,Fchaos.
OL,14,FThe motion was approved but only after
OL,15,FSir Lindsay Hoyle upended
OL,16,Fparliamentary convention by selecting
OL,17,FLabour's bid to amend an SNP motion on
OL,18,Fthe Israel-Hamas war.
