OL,6,FSir Lindsay said on Wednesday his
OL,7,Fdecision was based on concern about
OL,8,F"the security of all members and their
OL,9,Ffamilies".
OL,11,FThe Speaker suggested he had hoped a
OL,12,Fvote on all amendments would prevent
OL,13,Ffurther division over the wording of
OL,14,Fdifferent calls for a ceasefire.
OL,16,FAfter the SNP tabled a similar motion
OL,17,Fcalling for a ceasefire in Gaza in
OL,18,FNovember, many Labour MPs who
OL,19,Fabstained feared for their safety
OL,20,Fafter protests in their constituencies.
